    <item>
      <title>无证件次级借款人对华尔街构成风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/deportation-push-sows-hidden-risks-in-wall-street-s-debt-machine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马塞洛·罗德里格斯（Marcelo Rodriguez）正处于将华尔街与纽约说西班牙语社区联系起来的一系列贷款中间，为包括无证件的脆弱借款人提供了生命线。该生命线现在开始陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/deportation-push-sows-hidden-risks-in-wall-street-s-debt-machine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 13:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大人的纽约购物旅行逐渐消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/new-york-shopping-trips-by-canadians-dwindle-over-trump-s-taunts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，来自安大略省南部的加拿大人一直在跨境前往纽约布法罗的边界上，从而在Target和Trader Joe等零售商上加载了廉价的牛奶和商店，他们无法在家中使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/new-york-shopping-trips-by-canadians-dwindle-over-trump-s-taunts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
